This is the SYNTAX description.

aURL = action URL. This is the full http request needed to be made in order to get stuff done :)

	http://<gameURL>/game.php?<options>

<options> :	opt1, '&'
		opt...

		village : players current townID
		screen  : list of screentypes
			:	info_village : get's other Village info screen
				map : no other Village needed, will just pop to map for current Village
				overview : giev current town overview
		id	: other Village townID
		


	http://<gameURL>/place?<options>

<options> :	opt1, '&'
		opt...
	
		mode	: list of actions 
				:	command (send troops to target)
		target	: Target Village townID		